you would make me lose everything?

703
00:38:46,599 --> 00:38:48,119
What are you doing here?

704
00:38:48,119 --> 00:38:49,280
I don't want to talk to you.

705
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:50,719
Get out!

706
00:38:50,719 --> 00:38:53,199
I made a mistake before.

707
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:56,800
You're protected by the Floral Envoy.

708
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:58,760
A lowly person like me
can't afford to offend you.

709
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:00,440
I'm here

710
00:39:00,440 --> 00:39:01,840
