714
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,079
Coincidentally,

715
00:39:08,079 --> 00:39:09,679
I have taken on a birthday banquet.

716
00:39:10,239 --> 00:39:12,880
As long as you help me with that

717
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,320
