720
00:39:20,039 --> 00:39:21,679
It is laughable.

721
00:39:21,679 --> 00:39:23,360
Huamanzhu was mine.

722
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,360
You're doomed this time.

723
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:26,800
You're begging for help.

724
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:28,760
Yet you have the audacity
to sell my shop to me.

725
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,440
How do you know?

726
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:33,920
Generally, the birthday banquet for the noble

727
00:39:34,519 --> 00:39:36,239
is undertaken by the flower guild.

728
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:39,400
Do you know

729
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,599
why you

730
00:39:40,599 --> 00:39:42,320
